Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I am leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:42.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Futaba--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,"I Am Graduating from Bread Crusts"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:01:00.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko, did you hear? It's such a nice day,\Nbut it's supposed to rain in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ow, that hurts!\N--Wh-What is the matter with you, Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:13.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?\NWhat's the matter with {\i1}you{\i0}, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:15.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What is the matter with {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm tired and my body feels heavy.\NI'm so proud of myself for going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You are so polite!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:35.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It is a surprise, or what is it called?\NLike a candid camera ruse to surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:51.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodness gracious. I will not be tricked\Nby this. You can stop your act.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:58.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yoko is acting strange!\NShe said, "goodness gracious"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe {\i1}you're {\i0}saying that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I finished crocheting lace yesterday!\NIt took two whole months!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Crocheting lace? Why don't you just buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, this is my hobby.\NLook, isn't it just the cutest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:22.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh man, what a girly hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's the matter, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,They are even like this when I am not present.\NWhat is the matter with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hayama, w-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up, Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:48.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the last one to...\Nturn in the worksheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to turn all of them in at once, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot, I haven't done it yet. Why don't you do\Nit for me, Nishiyama? You're class rep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:02.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:06.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. This is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:11.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You're making it hard for Nishiyama\Nby not turning it in. Oh, Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:16.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, all right. I guess I'll do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What a terrible dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama. Oh, that Hayama! Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What a troublemaker! Curse her! I'll show her how\NI am when I'm not holding back. Just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:39.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Look how much trouble you're\Ngiving Nishiyama! Hurry up and turn it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:45.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama's not class representative\Nbecause she wants to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,She was forced to be class representative, because\Nnobody else wanted to do all the extra work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama's really timid,\Nso she couldn't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:58.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe they haven't changed all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel so lazy! Maybe I'll\Nditch afternoon classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That won't do! You should go to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So lazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I am still not used to these two like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if this is a dream,\Nwhat is everybody else like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:32.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoo! I'm so annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate the world! Maybe I'll\Nbreak all the school windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:44.37,Main,,0,0,0,,If I steal a motorcycle and don't know\Nhow to ride it, it's the world's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama's sister is the top\Nbad girl in this school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Bad girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,She even comes to school. Talk about devoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:00.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What, Nishikawa? Address your teachers properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?! Violence at school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko, what are you doing?\NYou just punched a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I could not help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.53,Main,,0,0,0,,But he's a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:28.87,Main,,0,0,0,,And I did not punch him.\NIt was a slap. Oh, goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted to clarify?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:36.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this?! It's an offense to hit a teacher!\NReport to the faculty room, immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,If there's a problem, they can come to {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you so rebellious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, now. What's the fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:54.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Class is starting soon.\NReturn to your classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:06:02.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe... you want to be\Npunished by Ms. Shino?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's what happened in the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That was {\i1}your {\i0}dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course it was. I would do no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it interesting? It's too bad I\Nwoke up right when it was getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't my personality pretty terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:35.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't too different from the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You weren't even there, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.27,Main,,0,0,0,,"Central Shopping Arcade"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Central Shopping Arcade"\NIt does seem pretty fun to be a different you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Especially since you're usually\Nhiding your real self, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:52.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, there she is! Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:07:00.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, how do I look? I tried changing my image!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:09.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it's pretty good, too. You know how\NI'm going to be an idol when I grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, you mentioned that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:20.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So, can you listen to me sing? I need to get used to\Nsinging in front of people, so I don't get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:23.61,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I'm in full bloom! My charm is never-ending! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I won't let you even glance at other girls! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,--♪ Today and tomorrow, forever and ever! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--U-Ugh... recital...\N--♪ Today and tomorrow, forever and ever! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--Unlike my sister, she's completely off...\N--♪ Today and tomorrow, forever and ever! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Sa-Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you practice before\Nperforming in front of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they say to wear a bucket\Non your head to cure your tone-deafness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:12.24,Main,,0,0,0,,A bucket... So I should sing with this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.50,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I'm in full bloom! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I'm in full bloo-- ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:33.10,Main,,0,0,0,,F-Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I might throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Good thing we have a bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:42.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried doing it like Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It does not get in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Want to try on glasses, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama. Glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Glasses aren't an optional feature for braids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should cut it shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:11.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you?! How could you cut your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:16.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be a good change.\NThe ends are damaged, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:21.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Long hair uses a lot of shampoo and\Nwater, which can get expensive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But. It would be a waste to cut your long hair.\NYou've been growing it out since you were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Right? It would be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't go back once you've cut it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Your normal hair style fits you best, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,A princess hair cut is a must for a rich girl,\Neven though you no longer are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Not because it looks good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:05.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I am not just so-so anymore! Do you not\Nthink I am a pro at working part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Miss Yoko. You're best in the\Nworld at anything you do. You're a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,A pro at working part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, at first, I couldn't believe\Nshe was working part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:24.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She probably grew quickly\Nbecause of this environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, found it! It's here!\NThis is the shop from the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:38.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Which one should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,A school friend... from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Osakabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, we were in the same grade\Nat my previous school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mannenro Girls' Academy,\Nright? The rich girl school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? Even rich girls work part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're learning how the world works?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I no longer have the\Nstanding to be a rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I am working for the income.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Strawberry Tart"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:52.34,Main,,0,0,0,,"Strawberry Tart"\NThese two cakes are our seasonal recommendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,"Strawberry Tart"\NOh. I'll have those, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. I'll have those, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:12:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko! Miss Yoko is a real pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You can contact me here, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me know if there is\Nanything I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.67,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:33.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You were amazing! A pro! You did your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Of course. I have leveled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,This is nothing! I am a pro part-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, even though all you have\Nis pride, you tried so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I will take a short break. I need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,That's mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard you had it rough yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:15.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It was fine. It is true that I do not want to be seen\Nlike this. But, I cannot go back to my old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Because, the me now is the actual me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful day it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Tee-he-he. He-he!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tee-he-he, ow ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:36.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Same reaction as in the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:39.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough feminine charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you say that when\Nyou're eating like {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Even {\i1}I'm {\i0}trying my best to\Nbecome an idol by doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba, why don't you put\Neffort into something, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I was shocked to hear that I didn't\Nhave enough feminine charm,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:06.14,Main,,0,0,0,,so I wanted to show people\Nthat I'm a girl. Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko is trying her best, so I\Nthought I could try my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:19.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! The birdies are having a little chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama is all polka-dotted! Are they hives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, these are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, do you want some, Odagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm satisfied from\Njust you offering! Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What's the matter, Odagiri?\NAre you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost lunch time, so I\Nshouldn't eat sweets now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?! They're burnt milk caramels!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You're drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're not very feminine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You should've just asked me for pointers.\NI do various things to better myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I take rose supplements to smell better,\Ndo stretches to maintain my figure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:20.67,Main,,0,0,0,,and regularly do sit-ups and use dumbbells.\NI also do {\i1}this {\i0}and {\i1}that {\i0}and {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You do that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You're fervently doing so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm trying hard! What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lucky Number" "Lucky Color"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lucky Number" "Lucky Color"\NMy lucky number's three. My lucky color is yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:36.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,At my horoscope. Girls like\Nchecking their horoscopes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:47.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Futaba Odagiri. You're not\Nstopping by Mr. Stuffed's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a new curry challenge.\NIf you finish three kilos, it's free!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Three! Yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.50,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not related.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm, I-I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:04.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't finish {\i1}three {\i0}kilos\Nof food. I {\i1}am {\i0}a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Are you\Ntrying to make a fool of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Futaba Odagiri! Don't say you can't\Nfinish it. It's rude to those who've lost to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. You are the best when\Nyou are shining brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Feminine charm is at absolute zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"\NThanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"\NI won't lose next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"\NFutaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:50.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard that you wanted to raise your feminine charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I made this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:17:01.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! It's probably a special soup that will\Nraise my feminine charm or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope! It's a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,The color! And the smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I have some for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.71,Main,,0,0,0,,...our feminine charm went up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what are you doing here so early, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:31.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Daddy has a job for your dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, for my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That's great, Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:37.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Having connections is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. How can I thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:46.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Then, maybe you'll sign\Na marriage application?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you know. It'll be just\Nfor fun, like playing pretend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, I would be okay with that anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go submit our marriage application.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:02.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been learning how to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:09.55,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Aren't you head over heels?! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like this is his fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I am the daughter of the Nishikawa Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:25.52,Main,,0,0,0,,My father is a company employee,\Nand I am his only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's so normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:33.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I am now the same as you. I will not be\Neasily captivated by food like before--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Nishikawa... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my return gift for Valentine's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.08,Main,,0,0,0,,"Dietary Supplement Cookies" "10 packs of 4 sticks"\NThis is my return gift for Valentine's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my return gift for Valentine's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it should be cookies, but I\Nwanted them to be useful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,A-A-Are these for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,She's super happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't White Day next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you still thinking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I am pitiful. I have not changed\Na bit since I met you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}have {\i0}changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,When we first met, you said, "Why are\Nyou eating here, too? How bothersome!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You were more like a rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, I thought, here is a protected species.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean, endangered species.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What? But there'd be a lot\Nif you look in the right places.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,When did we start talking about animals? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's an endangered species,\Nmaybe they'll go extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:51.15,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why we need to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, why have you been talking about animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Found another endangered species.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:19:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'd be annoying if\Nthere were a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:05.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What would be annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't they talking about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:11.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo is a different kind of protected species.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing that again, Sonobe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.72,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's a rare beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't feed the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:29.31,Main,,0,0,0,,A-And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,A-A dangerous, poisonous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama! Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:53.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I am graduating from bread crusts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:54.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:58.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I am trying an instant food today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yakisoba Noodles"\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Gah! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:10.56,Main,,0,0,0,,She's done it! She put the sauce in first!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:14.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What she said before... It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:16.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,She's sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:28.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It is not like I enjoy instant noodles.\NThey are such a hassle, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Bread crusts are more abundant\Nand taste delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You brought some?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much!"
